    array of matched elements.
    
    ### Example:
    
        // group numbers by their remainder modulo 3:

        [3,6,9,11,2,3] .. seq.groupBy(n->n%3) .. seq.each(console.log)
        // will print:
        // [ 0, [ 3, 6, 9 ] ]
        // [ 2, [ 11, 2 ] ]
        // [ 0, [ 3 ] ]

